%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Using%20too%20many%20AI%20tools%20at%20once%20can%20actually%20make%20you%20less%20productive%20and%20cause%20'brain%20fry%2C'%20study%20finds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20stock%20image%20of%20a%20person%20with%20a%20headache%20in%20an%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af2385d3e2f1aef36a40cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EResearchers%20at%20the%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%20say%20they%20have%20found%20a%20troubling%20phenomenon%20in%20workers%20who%20are%20using%20multiple%20AI%20agents%20at%20once.%3Cp%3Edowell%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EResearchers%20have%20found%20a%20potential%20warning%20sign%20among%20some%20workers%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20say%20that%20some%20employees%20are%20experiencing%20%26quot%3BAI%20brain%20fry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20brain%20fry%20happens%20when%20workers%20experience%20mental%20fog%20and%20other%20fatigue%20after%20pushing%20themselves%20too%20much.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20tools%20can%20boost%20productivity%2C%20but%20companies%20need%20to%20be%20wary%20of%20overdoing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study%20published%20in%20the%20Harvard%20Business%20Review%2C%20which%20surveyed%201%2C488%20full-time%20U.S.-based%20workers%20in%20large%20companies%20across%20a%20variety%20of%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%20a%20small%20but%20noticeable%20number%20of%20workers%20report%20experiencing%20mental%20fog%2C%20headaches%2C%20and%20slower%20decision-making%2C%20or%20what%20the%20authors%20call%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhbr.org%2F2026%2F03%2Fwhen-using-ai-leads-to-brain-fry%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAI%20brain%20fry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20look%20at%20this%20as%20kind%20of%20the%20canary%20in%20the%20coal%20mine%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthew%20Kropp%2C%20one%20of%20the%20study's%20lead%20authors%20and%20a%20managing%20director%20and%20senior%20partner%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbcg-boston-consulting-group-ai-products-development-agents-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBoston%20Consulting%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThose%20engineers%20that%20are%20the%20early%20adopters%2C%20that%20are%20doing%20the%20multi-agent%20orchestration%20are%20experiencing%20this%20effect%2C%20more%20and%20more%20people%20are%20trying%20to%20move%20up%20to%20that%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20particular%20note%2C%20the%20study%20found%20that%20AI%20tools%20can%20boost%20productivity%20but%20only%20to%20a%20certain%20extent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20one%20tool%20helping%20me%20weigh%20technical%20decisions%2C%20another%20spitting%20out%20drafts%20and%20summaries%2C%20and%20I%20kept%20bouncing%20between%20them%2C%20double-checking%20every%20little%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20senior%20engineer%20manager%20told%20the%20authors.%20%26quot%3BBut%20instead%20of%20moving%20faster%2C%20my%20brain%20just%20started%20to%20feel%20cluttered.%20Not%20physically%20tired%2C%20just%E2%80%A6%20crowded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20who%20go%20from%20one%20to%20two%20AI%20tools%20simultaneously%20experience%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20increase%20in%20productivity%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%20But%20the%20increase%20is%20smaller%20when%20they%20go%20from%20two%20to%20three%20tools%2C%20and%20then%20it%20decreases%20from%20three%20onward%2C%20illustrating%20that%20multitasking%20can%20have%20its%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20saying%20we%20shouldn't%20manage%20multiple%20agents%2C%26quot%3B%20Kropp%2C%20who%20is%20also%20chief%20AI%20officer%20of%20BCG's%20X%2C%20the%20firm's%20team%20of%20roughly%203%2C000%20engineers%20that%20build%20AI%20solutions%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20reality.%20This%20is%20how%20we%20will%20be%20working%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20jobs.%20You%20will%20have%20humans%20managing%20agents.%20I%20think%20what's%20important%20is%20that%20we%20are%20conscious%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20has%20this%20impact%20and%20that%20we%20manage%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKropp%20said%20that%20he%20and%20his%20coauthors%20wanted%20to%20distinguish%20between%20general%20career%20burnout%20and%20the%20specific%20AI-related%20fatigue%20some%20workers%20are%20beginning%20to%20experience%20as%20agentic%20AI%20transforms%20their%20jobs%20and%20their%20day-to-day%20routines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20specific%20effect%2C%20because%20what's%20happening%20is%2C%20in%20order%20to%20oversee%20an%20agent%20effectively%2C%20this%20actually%20a%20high-congitive%20load%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20something%20rote.%20If%20I'm%20a%20software%20engineer%2C%20I'm%20having%20it%20design%20and%20write%20code%20for%20me%20and%20it%20really%20matters%20what%20it%20does%2C%20the%20output%20has%20to%20be%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20stress%20of%20managing%20one%20agent%20is%20then%20amplified%20by%20each%20additional%20agent%2C%20to%20the%20point%20where%20workers%20reach%20a%20breaking%20point.%20It's%20why%20the%20authors%20say%20businesses%20should%20be%20diligent%20in%20crafting%20their%20AI%20policies%2C%20including%20allowing%20for%20breaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%2050%20times%20more%20productive%2C%20maybe%20I%20should%20be%2020%20times%20more%20productive%2C%20but%20have%20better%20mental%20health%20and%20not%20want%20to%20quit%2C%26quot%3B%20Kropp%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteve%20Yegge%2C%20a%20veteran%20software%20engineer%2C%20recently%20suggested%20imposing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineer-steve-yegge-ai-burnout-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E3-hour%20cap%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineer-steve-yegge-ai-burnout-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20use%20AI-assisted%20coding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20occurrence%20of%20%26quot%3BAI%20brain%20fry%26quot%3B%20doesn't%20mean%20companies%20should%20avoid%20AI%20adoption%2C%20Kropp%20said.%20The%20study%20also%20found%20that%20when%20AI%20is%20used%20to%20replace%20%26quot%3Broutine%20or%20repetitive%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20rate%20of%20burnout%20declines%2C%20even%20if%20workers'%20mental%20fatigue%20does%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20part%20of%20where%20it's%20coming%20from%20is%20people%20get%20how%20to%20use%20these%20tools%2C%20and%20they%20can't%20stop%20because%20it%20is%20so%20empowering%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20I%20think%20the%20tools%20are%20positive%2C%20we%20just%20have%20to%20manage%20the%20negatives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%2014%25%20of%20the%20workers%20surveyed%20said%20they%20were%20experiencing%20%26quot%3BAI%20brain%20fry%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20percentage%20of%20workers%20in%20industries%20varied%20widely.%20Employees%20in%20marketing%20(25.9%25)%2C%20human%20resources%20(19.3%25)%2C%20operations%20(17.9%25)%2C%20and%20software%20engineering%20(17.8%25)%20reported%20a%20much%20higher%20rate%20of%20%26quot%3BAI%20brain%20fry%26quot%3B%20than%20those%20in%20legal%20and%20compliance%20roles%2C%20which%20were%20at%20roughly%206%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20differences%2C%20Kropp%20said%2C%20are%20due%20in%20part%20to%20the%20adoption%20rates%20among%20industries%20as%20a%20whole.%20He%20said%20that%20nine%20months%20ago%2C%20AI%20agents%20didn't%20have%20the%20capabilities%20they%20do%20now%2C%20and%20based%20on%20the%20current%20rate%20of%20change%2C%20other%20industries%20are%20likely%20to%20experience%20the%20upheaval%20that%20software%20engineering%20and%20computer%20programming%20are%20going%20through%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20think%20about%20that%20sort%20of%20ladder%20of%20adoption%2C%20at%20least%20in%20enterprise%20organizations%2C%20you%20really%20have%20less%20than%205%25%20that%20are%20in%20those%20top%20two%20levels%20that%20are%20even%20using%20agents%20at%20all%2C%20let%20alone%20using%20multiple%20at%20a%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20it's%20still%20very%20early.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-brain-fry-study-agents-uses-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773144652000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af4bc182b35e2c04dd6423%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-brain-fry-study-agents-uses-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Researchers%20found%20a%20concerning%20occurrence%20when%20they%20surveyed%201%2C488%20full-time%20US%20workers%20about%20how%20they%20use%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-brain-fry-study-agents-uses-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20went%20to%20Ireland%20for%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day.%20I%20had%20a%20great%20time%2C%20but%20there%20are%205%20things%20I%20wish%20I'd%20known%20before%20my%20trip.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20holds%20a%20cocktail%20while%20standing%20in%20a%20bar%2C%20wearing%20a%20Guinness%20sweater%20and%20an%20Ireland%20hat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699b8052efb52c8bd0dea309%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222267%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Shammas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20loved%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fst-patricks-day-celebrated-differences-ireland-us-2022-3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecelebrating%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Dublin%2C%20but%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20known%20a%20few%20things%20beforehand.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20example%2C%20when%20traveling%20for%20a%20major%20event%2C%20it's%20never%20too%20early%20to%20start%20booking%20reservations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20the%20best%20views%20of%20the%20parade%20in%20Dublin%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20arrive%20early.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIreland%20is%20my%20favorite%20place%20I've%20traveled%20to%2C%20so%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20plan%20a%20trip%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraditional-irish-breakfast-recipe-review-st-patricks-day-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESt.%20Patrick's%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thinking%20it%20would%20be%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20celebrate%20the%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20experience%20was%20incredible%2C%20filled%20with%20parades%2C%20pints%20of%20Guinness%2C%20and%20everything%20glowing%20green%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20would%20have%20been%20even%20better%20if%20I%20had%20known%20five%20things%20beforehand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b152bff7-f840-4fef-ba2f-d96396408281%5C%22%3EDublin%20becomes%20incredibly%20crowded%20on%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223441%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Crowds%20of%20people%20wearing%20green%20hats%20outside%20Temple%20Bar%20in%20Dublin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e1e3ee8408f6671803110%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222581%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20crowds%20on%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20are%20often%20shoulder-to-shoulder.%3Cp%3EMarek_Godlewski%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisiting-dublin-tips-from-local-born-in-ireland%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisited%20Dublin%3C%2Fa%3E%20twice%20before%2C%20so%20I%20know%20the%20city%20can%20get%20crowded.%20However%2C%20I've%20never%20experienced%20crowds%20like%20those%20on%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20the%20streets%20and%20pubs%20were%20shoulder-to-shoulder%2C%20and%20I%20typically%20found%20myself%20waiting%2045%20minutes%20just%20to%20get%20a%20drink.%20At%20times%2C%20it%20felt%20hard%20to%20move%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20did%20it%20again%2C%20I'd%20spend%20the%20holiday%20somewhere%20like%20Galway%20instead%2C%20where%20it%20still%20feels%20festive%20but%20a%20little%20less%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8b98cf3-4af6-4aa4-bc9e-d79f52c0e5f5%5C%22%3EIt's%20never%20too%20early%20to%20start%20planning%20the%20trip%20and%20booking%20reservations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2211%20pints%20of%20Guinness%20with%20pictures%20of%20women%20in%20the%20foam.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699cb70a156648bc16a8be61%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222267%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20booked%20my%20ticket%20for%20the%20Guinness%20Storehouse%20two%20months%20in%20advance.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Shammas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20always%20good%20to%20plan%20ahead%20for%20a%20trip%2C%20but%20if%20a%20major%20holiday%20is%20involved%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20get%20started%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20After%20all%2C%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20travel%20to%20Ireland%20for%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20week%2C%20so%20tickets%20and%20reservations%20can%20fill%20up%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20I%20purchased%20my%20ticket%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguinness-storehouse-dublin-review-ireland-world-travel-awards-tourism-visit-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGuinness%20Storehouse%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20months%20in%20advance%2C%20but%20one%20member%20of%20our%20group%20waited%20until%20the%20day%20before%20our%20trip.%20Unfortunately%20for%20her%2C%20tickets%20were%20sold%20out%20for%20the%20entire%20time%20we%20were%20in%20Ireland%2C%20so%20she%20missed%20out%20on%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20that%20it's%20best%20to%20secure%20any%20must-do%20reservations%20and%20tickets%20right%20after%20booking%20the%20trip%2C%20even%20if%20that%20means%20purchasing%20them%20months%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d5048ff-58b9-49e7-a804-34250c19e9ab%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20best%20parade%20views%2C%20arrive%20very%20early%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224283%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20looks%20out%20a%20window%20in%20Dublin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699cb8f52237a6a8f0cdaf67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20ended%20up%20watching%20the%20parade%20from%20our%20Airbnb.%20%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Shammas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDublin%20hosts%20a%20huge%20parade%20for%20the%20holiday%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20attend.%20So%2C%20we%20got%20up%20early%20and%20planned%20to%20be%20out%20of%20the%20house%20around%209%20a.m.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20parade%20was%20scheduled%20to%20start%20at%20noon%2C%20we%20figured%20this%20would%20give%20us%20plenty%20of%20time%20to%20find%20a%20spot.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20we%20were%20getting%20ready%2C%20we%20could%20already%20see%20massive%20crowds%20forming%20from%20our%20Airbnb%20window%2C%20and%20we%20quickly%20realized%20we%20might%20be%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20we%20made%20it%20down%20to%20the%20street%2C%20there%20were%20so%20many%20people%20that%20we%20couldn't%20see%20anything%20at%20all.%20The%20city%20had%20also%20set%20up%20barriers%20and%20blocked%20off%20streets%2C%20so%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20even%20find%20our%20way%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20we%20watched%20some%20of%20the%20excitement%20from%20our%20window%2C%20then%20went%20into%20a%20nearby%20pub%20and%20caught%20the%20parade%20on%20TV%2C%20which%20honestly%20ended%20up%20being%20just%20as%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d2ca611-7f02-4cc2-9f05-6a91adf173fe%5C%22%3EIt's%20important%20to%20stay%20mindful%20of%20your%20belongings%2C%20especially%20when%20traveling%20for%20a%20major%20event%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20your%20belongings%20anywhere%20you%20travel%2C%20but%20this%20felt%20especially%20important%20when%20attending%20an%20event%20that%20draws%20large%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20before%20the%20holiday%2C%20we%20were%20on%20a%20tour%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fireland-spots-to-see-and-skip-from-visitor-on-budget-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Cliffs%20of%20Moher%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20our%20guide%20warned%20us%20to%20be%20extra%20careful%2C%20explaining%20that%20the%20celebrations%20can%20be%20an%20opportunity%20for%20pickpockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20recommended%20wearing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fireland-trip-what-to-pack-list-from-local-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecrossbody%20bag%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%20a%20money%20belt%20with%20hidden%20zipper%20pockets%2C%20or%20carrying%20a%20backpack%20with%20a%20pocket%20that%20sits%20against%20your%20back%20so%20it's%20harder%20for%20people%20to%20get%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20warning%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20valid%2C%20because%20the%20next%20day%2C%20one%20of%20my%20friends%20had%20her%20phone%20stolen%20out%20of%20her%20pocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20reminder%20that%20it's%20better%20to%20take%20extra%20precautions%2C%20purchase%20the%20necessary%20accessories%2C%20and%20ensure%20nothing%20valuable%20is%20within%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224b3bcd5-9286-4e86-9bfa-cba6a90ea539%5C%22%3EThe%20celebrations%20start%20early%20in%20the%20week%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20walks%20down%20a%20street%20in%20Dublin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699cbbca2237a6a8f0cdafbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223214%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20wish%20we%20had%20arrived%20in%20Dublin%20earlier%20to%20take%20full%20advantage%20of%20the%20celebrations.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Shammas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20landed%20in%20Dublin%20on%20March%2015%2C%20the%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20celebrations%20were%20already%20in%20full%20swing.%20After%20exploring%20the%20area%20and%20chatting%20with%20locals%2C%20we%20learned%20that%20the%20celebrations%20start%20well%20before%20the%2017th.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowing%20that%2C%20we%20would've%20planned%20to%20arrive%20even%20earlier%20in%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20holiday%20passes%2C%20it's%20over%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20real%20excitement%20builds%20in%20the%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20it.%20So%2C%20arriving%20ahead%20of%20time%20allows%20for%20ample%20time%20to%20experience%20the%20festivities%20and%20fun%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fst-patricks-day-ireland-what-not-to-do-mistakes-dublin-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773144421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699b8052efb52c8bd0dea309%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fst-patricks-day-ireland-what-not-to-do-mistakes-dublin-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20a%20few%20things%20I%20wish%20I'd%20known%20before%20celebrating%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20in%20Dublin.%20For%20example%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20book%20reservations%20ahead%20of%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Amanda%20Shammas)%22%2C%22engage