3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20neurodivergent%20founders%20share%20how%20AI%20supports%20executive%20function%20and%20growth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rita%20Ramakrishnan%3B%20Chris%20Haddox%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af1b5efd4fbd083f29c82a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanice%20Chung%3B%20Matt%20Williams%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20neurodivergent%20entrepreneurs%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20can%20be%20a%20boon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETwo%20founders%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20AI%20helps%20them%20with%20scheduling%20and%20organization.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20also%20helps%20one%20founder%20rehearse%20for%20important%20meetings%20outside%20her%20comfort%20zone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Rita%20Ramakrishnan%20first%20started%20her%20executive%20coaching%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iksana.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIksana%20Consulting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20all%20of%20the%20new%20skills%20she%20needed%20to%20hone%20came%20easily.%20As%20a%20solopreneur%20with%20autism%20and%20ADHD%2C%20certain%20operational%20basics%20of%20running%20a%20business%20were%20more%20difficult%20for%20her%20than%20for%20some%20of%20her%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything%20that%20requires%20being%20on%20a%20specific%20schedule%2C%20anything%20that%20requires%20deep%20organization%2C%20those%20things%20were%20really%20challenging%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20Ramakrishnan%20said%20that%20she%20now%20has%20the%20help%20she%20needs%20to%20stay%20solo.%20%26quot%3BAI%20has%20become%20my%20external%20executive%20function%2C%20compensating%20for%20what%20my%20brain%20doesn't%20do%20well%20so%20I%20can%20lean%20harder%20into%20what%20it%20does%20brilliantly%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramakrishnan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20integrating%20AI%20into%20her%20workflows%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20she%20has%20grown%20her%20business%20revenue%20while%20being%20a%20graduate%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20enough%20people%20are%20talking%20about%20how%20AI%20is%20opening%20up%20market%20opportunities%20for%20neurodivergent%20folks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamakrishnan%20and%20another%20neurodivergent%20solopreneur%2C%20Chris%20Haddox%2C%20founder%20of%20clothing%20brand%20DECOY%20LTD%2C%20shared%20the%20specific%20ways%20they%20have%20integrated%20AI%20to%20streamline%20their%20work%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%2211648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chris%20Haddox%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af1bced3e2f1aef36a3fd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%228736%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Williams%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a6df8911-5f62-4422-959b-2af5bf4eb614%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20helps%20with%20task%20and%20energy%20management%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERamakrishnan's%20AI%20workflow%20starts%20first%20thing%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20when%20she%20dumps%20everything%20on%20her%20mind%20into%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20or%20Google's%20Gemini%20and%20has%20the%20generative%20AI%20tools%20organize%20the%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20helps%20me%20move%20from%20a%20jumbled%20place%20where%20I'm%20at%20first%20thing%20in%20the%20morning%20into%20a%20synthesized%20and%20organized%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20uses%20a%20similar%20process%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20client%20project%2C%20putting%20unstructured%20thoughts%20into%20an%20AI%20chat%20and%20asking%20it%20to%20organize%20them%20into%20a%20thoughtful%20project%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20she%20transfers%20the%20information%20into%20the%20productivity%20tool%20Motion%2C%20which%20can%20schedule%20reminders%20and%20add%20tasks%20to%20her%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20basic%20task%20management%2C%20Ramakrishnan%20uses%20AI%20to%20plan%20for%20the%20energy%20swings%20she%20experiences%20throughout%20the%20day%20as%20a%20neurodivergent%20person.%20%26quot%3BIt%20knows%20when%20to%20schedule%20things%20based%20on%20when%20my%20energy%20levels%20are%20high%20or%20low%2C%20and%20based%20on%20what%20types%20of%20tasks%20I%20gain%20further%20energy%20from%20that%20I%20love%20doing%20and%20tasks%20that%20I%20deeply%20hate%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%229504%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rita%20Ramakrishnan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af1c01fd4fbd083f29c847%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanice%20Chung%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20this%2C%20Ramakrishnan%20said%20she%20had%20both%20Claude%20and%20Gemini%20track%20her%20daily%20energy%20for%20a%20few%20weeks.%20Then%2C%20she%20built%20custom%20projects%20in%20each%20tool%20based%20on%20how%20they%20synthesized%20her%20energy%20patterns.%20Now%20she%20can%20drop%20tasks%20into%20each%20LLM%2C%20and%20they%20will%20suggest%20an%20optimal%20time%20for%20each%20one%2C%20Ramakrishnan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20knows%20that%20if%20I%20have%20to%20write%20proposals%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Monday%2C%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20Thursdsay%20afternoons%20are%20the%20best%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a755727b-6010-4956-8e26-864722ce9ff8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20helps%20founders%20stay%20focused%20and%20organize%20information%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Haddox%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdecoy.ltd%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDECOY%20LTD.%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20intentionally%20avoids%20using%20AI%20for%20the%20creative%20and%20artistic%20aspects%20of%20his%20work%2C%20he's%20found%20it%20useful%20for%20keeping%20him%20on%20track%20as%20a%20solopreneur%20with%20ADHD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20stay%20focused%20on%20one%20train%20of%20thought.%20It's%20very%20easy%20to%20want%20to%20get%20my%20hands%20on%20everything%20in%20front%20of%20me%20when%20initially%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20solve%20one%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20Haddox%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227954%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chris%20Haddox%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af1dafd3e2f1aef36a402c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%229943%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Williams%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20having%20a%20conversation%20with%20another%20person%20can%20keep%20him%20focused%2C%20but%20since%20a%20second%20party%20isn't%20always%20available%2C%20a%20back-and-forth%20with%20AI%20can%20help%20fill%20that%20gap.%20For%20example%2C%20he%20might%20go%20to%20Claude%20with%20a%20technical%20bug%20and%20get%20a%20reminder%20of%20a%20solution%20that's%20worked%20in%20the%20past%2C%20industry%20best%20practices%20he%20wouldn't%20know%20otherwise%2C%20or%20additional%20questions%20he%20didn't%20think%20to%20ask.%20%26quot%3BIt%20certainly%20organizes%20my%20thoughts%20better%20than%20I%20ever%20could%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he's%20found%20this%20especially%20valuable%20as%20someone%20balancing%20running%20his%20business%20on%20the%20side%20with%20a%20full-time%20job.%20%26quot%3BBeing%20able%20to%20come%20home%20after%20work%20and%20pick%20up%20where%20I%20left%20off%20on%20a%20chat%20that%20maybe%20I%20had%20even%20last%20week%2C%20without%20any%20sort%20of%20error%2C%20is%20really%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb0d1a85-2766-4cb1-a5ba-d15cd7b03cef%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20supports%20sales%20and%20networking%20prep%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20even%20helped%20Ramakrishnan%20improve%20at%20one-to-one%20human%20conversations%2C%20which%20are%20necessary%20for%20growing%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPut%20me%20in%20a%20coaching%20session%20and%20I%20am%20my%20best%20self.%20Put%20me%20in%20a%20sales%20conversation%20and%20I'm%20an%20awkward%20turtle%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20autism%20talking%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226336%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rita%20Ramakrishnan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af1ddbd3e2f1aef36a4033%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%229504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJanice%20Chung%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20scale%20her%20business%2C%20she%20knew%20she%20had%20to%20get%20better%20at%20these%20types%20of%20calls%2C%20so%20she%20uses%20AI%20to%20aggregate%20online%20information%20about%20who%20she's%20meeting%20with%2C%20and%20then%20rehearses%20different%20scenarios%20for%20pitching%20her%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20autistic%20brain%20loves%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramakrishnan%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20research%20puts%20her%20at%20ease%20and%20makes%20her%20feel%20more%20equipped%20to%20somewhat%20predict%20what%20the%20person%20might%20need%20or%20empathize%20with%20what%20they're%20facing.%20She%20said%20that%20she%20uses%20the%20same%20process%20to%20prepare%20for%20conferences%20and%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20using%20AI%20to%20be%20more%20productive.%20I'm%20using%20it%20to%20stop%20punishing%20myself%20for%20how%20my%20brain%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramakrishnan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20hre