d%20in%20March.%20The%20movie%20features%20a%20star-studded%20cast.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fjailer-2-shah-rukh-khans-role-in-rajinikanths-film-revealed-nelson-film-gets-a-massive-pan-india-boost%2Farticleshow%2F129390735.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bill%20Ackman's%20hedge%20fund%2C%20Pershing%20Square%2C%20just%20filed%20for%20an%20IPO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bill%20Ackman%20attends%202025%20Pershing%20Square%20Foundation%20MIND%20and%20Cancer%20Prize%20Award%20Dinner%20at%20The%20Pool%20on%20May%2022%2C%202025%20in%20New%20York.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698ccdf8a645d11881892642%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBill%20Ackman.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Ostuni%2FPatrick%20McMullan%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBill%20Ackman's%20hedge%20fund%2C%20Pershing%20Square%2C%20is%20going%20public.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20said%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20statement%20that%20it%20has%20filed%20for%20an%20IPO%20on%20the%20NYSE.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPershing%20Square%20is%20seeking%20to%20raise%20at%20least%20%245%20billion%20in%20the%20IPO%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPershing%20Square%2C%20the%20investment%20fund%20run%20by%20famed%20investor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-newsletter-bill-ackman-one-liner-dating-advice-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBill%20Ackman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20filed%20for%20an%20IPO%2C%20it%20announced%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAckman's%20fund%20is%20planning%20a%20dual%20listing%20of%20Pershing%20Square%20Capital%20Management%20and%20a%20closed-end%20investment%20company%2C%20Pershing%20Square%20USA%2C%20on%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20seeking%20to%20raise%20at%20least%20%245%20billion%20for%20Pershing%20Square%20USA%20in%20the%20IPO%2C%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20announcing%20the%20planned%20listing.%20It%20has%20already%20secured%20%242.8%20billion%20from%20a%20private%20placement.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShares%20will%20be%20priced%20at%20%2450%20each%2C%20it%20added.%2020%20shares%20in%20Pershing%20Square%20Capital%20Management%20will%20be%20given%20for%20every%20100%20shares%20in%20Pershing%20Square%20USA%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20planned%20companies%20will%20be%20listed%20under%20the%20stock%20market%20tickers%20%26quot%3BPS%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BPSUS%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20securities%20will%20trade%20separately%2C%20but%20the%20dual%20listing%20status%20will%20offer%20investors%20individual%20paths%20to%20participate%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20Pershing%20Square%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pershing%20Square%20platform%20oversees%20a%20concentrated%20portfolio%20of%20large-cap%20companies%20like%20Meta%2C%20Alphabet%2C%20and%20Uber.%20It%20has%20assets%20under%20management%20of%20%2428.3%20billion%20as%20of%20February%202026%2C%20most%20of%20which%20is%20concentrated%20in%208%20to%2012%20core%20holdings%2C%20according%20to%20its%20most%20recent%20annual%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Pershing%20Square%20invested%20roughly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-pershing-square-meta-stake-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E10%25%20of%20its%20capital%20in%20Meta%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ackman%20described%20Meta%20as%20a%20primary%20beneficiary%20of%20AI%20integration%20that%20was%20trading%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20discounted%20valuation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20IPO%20is%20an%20unusual%20move%20for%20a%20hedge%20fund.%20Hedge%20fund%20performance%20can%20be%20volatile%2C%20and%20an%20IPO%20will%20lift%20the%20shroud%20of%20secrecy%20that%20hedge%20funds%20are%20generally%20accustomed%20to.%20But%20Ackman%20has%20grown%20his%20personal%20brand%20and%20become%20outspoken%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fackman-trump-call-cap-credit-card-interest-mistake-affordability-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeconomy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-donates-alex-pretti-family-after-fatal-shooting-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epolitics%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pershing%20CEO%20has%20previously%20indicated%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20make%20Pershing%20the%20next%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%2C%20the%20multinational%20investment%20vehicle%20that%2C%20until%20January%202026%2C%20was%20led%20by%20legendary%20investor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-successor-greg-abel-salary-berkshire-hathaway-stock-pledge-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWarren%20Buffett%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-investment-fund-pershing-square-files-for-an-ipo-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773139258000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aff284441e48aec3a1cadc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-investment-fund-pershing-square-files-for-an-ipo-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Famed%20investor%20Bill%20Ackman%20is%20taking%20his%20hedge%20fund%20public%2C%20planning%20a%20listing%20on%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Will%20Martin%2CPolly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-investment-fund-pershing-square-files-for-an-ipo-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22