uters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20war%20in%20Iran%20is%20already%20disrupting%20travel%20with%20flight%20cancellations%20and%20higher%20fuel%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20conflict%20could%20also%20disrupt%20Dubai's%20status%20as%20a%20safe%20global%20travel%20hub.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20say%20Dubai's%20travel%20industry%20relies%20on%20safety%2C%20and%20air%20routes%20could%20shift%20if%20war%20continues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDubai's%20status%20as%20a%20global%20travel%20hub%20and%20luxury%20tourist%20destination%20is%20being%20tested%2C%20as%20the%20US%20and%20Israeli%20conflict%20with%20Iran%20disrupts%20air%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20over%20a%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-proving-ground-for-newest-us-weapons-missile-drone-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einto%20the%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thousands%20of%20flights%20have%20been%20canceled%20or%20rerouted%2C%20the%20price%20of%20oil%20has%20surged%2C%20and%20United%20Airlines%20CEO%20Scott%20Kirby%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20increases%20to%20airfare%20prices%20would%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20start%20quick%2C%26quot%3B%20following%20the%20spike%20in%20fuel%20prices%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2026%2F03%2F06%2Funited-airlines-ceo-scott-kirby.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20prices%20surpassed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-price-shock-brent-wti-crude-100-threshold-iran-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24100%20a%20barrel%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20weekend%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%20in%202022%2C%20though%20prices%20dipped%20to%20roughly%20%2486%20a%20barrel%20late%20Monday.%20At%20the%20start%20of%202026%2C%20Brent%20crude%20oil%20was%20roughly%20%2460%20per%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnna%20Abelson%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20New%20York%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20week%20that%20if%20Dubai%20loses%20its%20reputation%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20haven%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bseamless%20transfer%20hub%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20effects%20could%20ripple%20throughout%20the%20industry.%20Travelers%20could%20look%20for%20alternative%20routes%2C%20and%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20length%20of%20the%20volatility%20in%20the%20region%2C%20airlines%20could%20change%20their%20routes%20to%20layover%20in%20other%20cities%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20unprecedented%2C%26quot%3B%20Abelson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20brace%20for%20impact%2C%20sadly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDubai%20has%20spent%20decades%20building%20a%20reputation%20as%20an%20attractive%2C%20safe%2C%20and%20luxurious%20destination%20for%20tourists%2C%20ultimately%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20most%20visited%20cities%20in%20the%20world%20and%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20travel%20hubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmirates%2C%20known%20for%20being%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femirates-airbus-a350-rival-boeing-777x-cabins-features-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eluxurious%20airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20its%20global%20hub%20at%20the%20Dubai%20International%20Airport%2C%20a%20common%20layover%20on%20itineraries%20connecting%20Europe%2C%20Africa%2C%20and%20Asia%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdubai-international-airport-dxb-attack-evacuated-injuries-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDubai%20International%20Airport%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20second-busiest%20airport%20worldwide%20in%202024%20in%20total%20number%20of%20passengers%2C%20just%20behind%20Atlanta%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20Airports%20Council%20International%20World.%20For%20international%20passengers%20specifically%2C%20it%20was%20the%20busiest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20industry%20experts%20agreed%20that%20changes%20to%20Dubai's%20reputation%20could%20have%20reverberating%20impacts%2C%20though%20they%20said%20that%20its%20status%20as%20a%20travel%20hub%20will%20depend%20on%20how%20long%20the%20conflict%20drags%20on%20and%20the%20ultimate%20outcome%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20tourism%20101%2C%26quot%3B%20Alan%20Fyall%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Central%20Florida%20and%20an%20expert%20in%20tourism%20destination%20marketing%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20week.%20%26quot%3BAnywhere%20in%20the%20world%20only%20works%20for%20tourism%20if%20you're%20stable%20and%20you're%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFyall%20said%20Dubai%20has%20been%20an%20incredibly%20safe%20place%20to%20visit%2C%20but%20that%20many%20tourists%20may%20not%20have%20realized%20its%20proximity%20to%20Iran.%20That's%20likely%20to%20change%20now%20after%20Iran%20targeted%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20city%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-damage-luxury-tourism-dubai-fairmont-palm-iran-airstrike-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estrikes%20damaging%20the%20airport%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20two%20luxury%20hotels.%20Tourists%20stranded%20in%20the%20city%20last%20week%20could%20hear%20loud%20booms%20as%20missiles%20were%20intercepted.%20That%20could%20make%20tourists%20think%20twice%20about%20visiting%2C%20particularly%20during%20times%20of%20increased%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaren%20and%20Bob%20Carifee%2C%20a%20married%20couple%20from%20Texas.%20got%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-couple-stuck-dubai-cruise-canceled-cant-get-help-us-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estuck%20in%20Dubai%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20after%20their%20cruise%20was%20canceled.%20The%20couple%20said%20they.%20heard%20missiles%20get%20intercepted%20and%20witnessed%20the%20luxury%20Fairmont%20get%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20long%20the%20war%20will%20last.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20previously%20said%20it%20could%20last%20weeks.%20On%20Monday%2C%20he%20said%20the%20war%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20complete%2C%20pretty%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20later%20suggested%20there%20was%20more%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20conflict%20continues%2C%20travelers%20could%20prefer%20routes%20that%20go%20through%20other%20cities%2C%20like%20London%2C%20Frankfurt%2C%20or%20Istanbul%2C%20where%20there's%20less%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlp%20Ozaman%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20New%20York%20University%20and%20a%20marketing%20manager%20for%20Turkish%20Airlines%2C%20said%20the%20problem%20will%20be%20whether%20tourists%20remember%20this%20episode%20and%20consider%20places%20like%20Dubai%20safe%20in%20the%20future.%20%26quot%3BThe%20memory%20of%20this%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20regards%20to%20travelers%20stuck%20at%20airports%20and%20on%20cruise%20ships%20over%20the%20past%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOzaman%20said%20countries%20like%20the%20UAE%20have%20invested%20too%20much%20in%20tourism%20and%20will%20take%20concerted%20efforts%20to%20win%20visitors%20back%20if%20there%20is%20a%20hit%20to%20the%20industry.%20%26quot%3BThey%20will%20not%20just%20throw%20their%20hands%20up%20and%20give%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20said%20what%20happens%20next%20is%20not%20entirely%20in%20their%20hands.%20%26quot%3BThese%20countries%20are%20really%20good%20in%20marketing%3A%20UAE%2C%20Qatar%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20but%20they%20can't%20control%20the%20situation%20with%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20how%20this%20conflict%20ultimately%20ends%20and%20whether%20there%20is%20regime%20change%20in%20Iran%20could%20also%20impact%20whether%20tourists%20return%20to%20the%20Gulf%20or%20try%20to%20avoid%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Carifees%20from%20Texas%20said%20they'd%20be%20open%20to%20returning%20in%20the%20future.%20They%20said%20they%20felt%20relatively%20safe%20and%20that%20the%20government%20has%20been%20doing%20a%20lot%20to%20reassure%20residents%20and%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFyall%20said%20he%20feels%20for%20Dubai%20and%20other%20tourism%20destinations%20in%20the%20region%20because%20they%20have%20so%20much%20to%20offer%20visitors%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it's%20stability%2C%20and%20it's%20safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20are%20the%20two%20words%20that%20drive%20tourism%20anywhere%20on%20the%20planet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdubai-safe-travel-hub-airan-war-fuel-prices-route-changes-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773136981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af6f71ccda166eed3d0d72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdubai-safe-travel-hub-airan-war-fuel-prices-route-changes-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Iran%20war%20is%20already%20raising%20fuel%20prices%20and%20could%20impact%20Dubai's%20status%20as%20a%20global%20travel%20hub%2C%20which%20relies%20on%20its%20reputation%20for%20safety.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdubai-safe-travel-hub-airan-war-fuel-prices-route-changes-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20A%20Person%20Takes%20Bribe%2C%20He%20Acquires%20Proceeds%20Of%20Crime%26quot%3B%3A%20Bombay%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20person%20acquires%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20if%20he%20takes%20a%20bribe%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20while%20refusing%20relief%20to%20a%20former%20senior%20official%20of%20the%20Vasai%20Virar%20City%20Municipal%20Corporation%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20last%20year%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773136935000%2C%22vis