%20built%20much%20of%20the%20communication%20network%20that%20US%20households%20and%20businesses%20rely%20on%20every%20day%2C%20and%20now%20it's%20rebuilding%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20150-year-old%20company%20said%20Tuesday%20it%20is%20investing%20%24250%20billion%20to%20modernize%20its%20US%20telecom%20infrastructure%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20phone%20call%20sparked%20an%20entirely%20new%20way%20for%20people%20and%20businesses%20to%20deepen%20connections%20and%20thrive%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-ceo-john-stankey-email-employee-feedback-survey-rto-policy-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20John%20Stankey%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20we%20carry%20the%20spirit%20of%20communication%20forward%20in%20bold%20new%20ways%2C%20powering%20connections%20for%20a%20new%20generation%20%E2%80%94%20more%20instantaneous%2C%20seamless%2C%20and%20limitless%20than%20ever%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20competitor%20Verizon%20reported%20spending%20%2417%20billion%20on%20capital%20expenditures%20last%20year%20and%20projected%20%2416.5%20billion%20this%20year%2C%20a%20figure%20it%20says%20puts%20the%20company%20in%20the%20top%2010%20investors%20in%20data%20infrastructure%2C%20apart%20from%20those%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-locations-us-map-ai-boom-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-hardcore-era-employee-changes-att-memo-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecome%20a%20long%20way%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20century%20and%20a%20half%20since%20inventor%20and%20entrepreneur%20Alexander%20Graham%20Bell%20linked%20the%20first%20pair%20of%20telephones%20with%20a%20copper%20wire.%20Now%2C%20AT%26amp%3BT%20says%20voice%20calls%20account%20for%20only%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20the%20traffic%20on%20its%20network%2C%20which%20is%20now%20dominated%20by%20text%20and%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20demands%20are%20only%20going%20up%20from%20here%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20to%20increase%20the%20need%20for%20dense%20fiber%20networks%20and%20more%20symmetrical%20connectivity%20into%20and%20out%20of%20homes%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20devices%2C%26quot%3B%20Stankey%20said%20during%20AT%26amp%3BT's%20earnings%20call%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20video%20streaming%2C%20which%20mostly%20requires%20one-way%20data%20downloads%2C%20cloud-based%20AI%20computing%20and%20remote%20work%20require%20a%20much%20more%20robust%20upload%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT's%20answer%20to%20that%20growing%20demand%20is%20to%20decommission%20its%20sprawling%20web%20of%20copper%20wires%20and%20replace%20them%20with%20a%20combination%20of%20fiber-optic%20cable%2C%205G%20wireless%2C%20and%20satellite%20links.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-moving-global-hq-dallas-suburbs-memo-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDallas-based%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20this%20approach%20will%20bring%20faster%20speeds%20to%20users%20in%20urban%2C%20suburban%2C%20and%20rural%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20strengthening%20its%20responders%20network%20for%20public%20safety%20and%20resilience%2C%20called%20FirstNet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStankey%20has%20also%20credited%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20favorable%20tax%20and%20regulatory%20policies%20for%20facilitating%20the%20upgrades%20now%2C%20including%20depreciation%20provisions%20of%20the%20One%20Big%2C%20Beautiful%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCurrent%20Federal%20telecommunications%20policy%20is%20as%20strong%20as%20I've%20seen%20in%20my%20career%2C%20making%20our%20commitment%20to%20invest%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20Tuesday's%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3