%20could%20have%20a%20very%20significant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-recession-prediction-mark-zandi-gdp-growth-labor-market-stocks-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecession%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202027%20because%20business%20spending%20will%20face%20a%20vacuum%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%2C%20after%20Americans%20receive%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tax-law-changes-may-mean-bigger-refunds-for-filers-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etax%20refunds%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%2C%20the%20economy%20could%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Blifeline%26quot%3B%20of%20two%20to%20three%20months%20before%20potentially%20seeing%20more%20serious%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiscal%20and%20AI-related%20stimulus%20have%20been%20key%20to%20powering%20the%20economy%20in%20recent%20years.%20For%20one%2C%20the%20US%20got%20a%20substantial%20boost%20from%20President%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-big-beautiful-bill-impacts-wallet-taxes-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOne%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20extended%20the%202017%20tax%20cuts%20and%20introduced%20a%20slate%20of%20other%20fiscal%20policies%20aimed%20at%20stimulating%20the%20economy.%20Over%20the%20long%20run%2C%20the%20bill%20was%20expected%20to%20boost%20GDP%20by%201.2%20percentage%20points%2C%20according%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftaxfoundation.org%2Fblog%2Fwill-the-obbba-tax-cuts-grow-the-us-economy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimate%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Tax%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Rosenberg%20thinks%20that%20stimulus%20comes%20into%20jeopardy%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmidterm-elections-stock-market-outlook-volatility-healthcare-stocks-trump-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emidterm%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20November%2C%20referring%20