%20inference%20compute%20they%20will%20have%20to%20build%20with%20Codex%2C%26quot%3B%20Thibault%20Sottiaux%2C%20engineering%20lead%20at%20OpenAI's%20Codex%2C%20the%20startup's%20AI%20coding%20service%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20usage%20per%20user%20is%20growing%20much%20faster%20than%20overall%20user%20growth%2C%20a%20sign%20that%20AI%20compute%20is%20becoming%20even%20scarcer%20and%20more%20valuable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20scarcity%20is%20reshaping%20how%20engineers%20think%20about%20their%20work%20and%20pay.%20OpenAI%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-cofounder-greg-brockman-engineer-trait-technical-humility-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGreg%20Brockman%3C%2Fa%3E%20put%20it%20bluntly%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20inference%20compute%20available%20to%20you%20is%20increasingly%20going%20to%20drive%20overall%20software%20productivity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20access%20to%20AI%20may%20soon%20matter%20as%20much%20as%20access%20to%20a%20fat%20salary%20and%20juicy%20equity%20awards.%20As%20a%20coder%20in%20the%20AI%20era%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20access%20to%20massive%20compute%2C%20you%20might%20end%20up%20producing%20far%20less%20software%20than%20your%20colleagues%2C%20threatening%20your%20career%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHakeem%20Shibly%2C%20a%20data%20specialist%20at%20Levels.fyi%2C%20recently%20spotted%20a%20compensation%20submission%20from%20a%20software%20engineer%20that%20listed%20%26quot%3BCopilot%20subscription%26quot%3B%20as%20part%20of%20the%20pay%20and%20benefits%2C%20a%20small%20but%20symbolic%20step%20toward%20AI%20access%20as%20a%20standard%20perk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276e962da-c549-467a-a250-78e84672b7fb%5C%22%3EGetting%20paid%20in%20AI%20tokens%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20in%20the%20AI%20community%20see%20an%20even%20more%20explicit%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20should%20create%20recruitment%20sites%20where%20their%20clients%20can%20advertise%20roles%2C%20listing%20the%20token%20budget%20for%20the%20job%20alongside%20the%20salary%20range%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Peter%20Gostev%2C%20AI%20capability%20lead%20at%20Arena%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20measures%20the%20performance%20of%20models.%20Those%20startups%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20taking%20note.%20Tomasz%20Tunguz%20of%20Theory%20Ventures%20said%20companies%20are%20effectively%20adding%20AI%20inference%20as%20a%20fourth%20component%20of%20engineering%20compensation%3A%20salary%2C%20bonus%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-ai-factory-tokens-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enow%20tokens%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETokens%20are%20the%20economic%20language%20of%20generative%20AI.%20Models%20break%20down%20words%20and%20other%20inputs%20into%20numerical%20tokens%20to%20make%20them%20easier%20to%20process%20and%20understand.%20One%20token%20is%20about%20%C2%BE%20of%20a%20word.%20They're%20also%20used%20to%20price%20AI%20model%20use%2C%20via%20an%20industry-standard%20cost%20per%20million%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20you%20be%20paid%20in%20tokens%3F%20In%202026%2C%20you%20likely%20will%20start%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Tunguz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eeb43864-0e41-4b67-9e51-0139d9a2a87a%5C%22%3ECFOs%20are%20watching%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20CFOs%2C%20this%20potentially%20big%20new%20expense%20must%20be%20tracked%20as%20closely%20as%20other%20headcount-related%20costs%2C%20Tunguz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20starting%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Tunguz%20told%20me%2C%20as%20employee%20use%20of%20AI%20increasingly%20contributes%20to%20total%20cash%20burn.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20consideration%20for%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20CFO.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Levels.fyi%20pegging%20the%2075th%20percentile%20software%20en