2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129384159.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDirector%20RJ%20Balaji%20has%20clarified%20that%20the%20Suriya%20and%20Trisha%20starrer%20'Karuppu'%20will%20not%20release%20on%20April%2010%2C%20denying%20any%20producer%20dispute.%20He%20assured%20fans%20that%20after%20two%20years%20of%20dedicated%20work%2C%20an%20official%20release%20date%20and%20other%20key%20updates%20will%20be%20announced%20within%20ten%20days%2C%20promising%20the%20wait%20will%20be%20worthwhile.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22He%20worked%20at%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20OpenAI.%20He%20recommends%203%20steps%20to%20find%20success%20in%20Big%20Tech.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google's%20headquarters%20and%20campus.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af34c882b35e2c04dd627a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI's%20Michael%20Bolin%20(not%20pictured)%20previously%20worked%20at%20Google%20and%20Meta.%3Cp%3EBrooks%20Kraft%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20staffer%20Michael%20Bolin%20shared%20his%20three%20tips%20for%20succeeding%20in%20Big%20Tech.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBefore%20working%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20Bolin%20spent%20several%20years%20at%20both%20Meta%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20more%20you%20can%20follow%20these%20tips%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20more%20successful%20you're%20going%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Bolin%20said%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Peterman%20Pod.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20hit%20a%20tech%20trifecta%2C%20working%20at%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20OpenAI.%20He%20has%20some%20advice%20for%20finding%20success%20in%20Big%20Tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Bolin%20is%20the%20tech%20lead%20on%20Codex%2C%20OpenAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenais-codex-lead-shares-tips-engineers-stand-out-email-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoding%20assistant%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Before%20joining%20Sam%20Altman's%20AI%20giant%20in%202024%2C%20Bolin%20spent%20almost%2012%20years%20at%20Meta%2C%20per%20his%20LinkedIn.%20Before%20that%2C%20he%20worked%20at%20Google%20on%20tools%20that%20have%20stood%20the%20test%20of%20time%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-calendar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany's%20Calendar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhN5ZFzWFhhg%26t%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Peterman%20Pod%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Bolin%20shared%20three%20steps%20for%20making%20an%20impact%20in%20Big%20Tech.%20While%20they're%20certainly%20helpful%20at%20companies%20like%20Google%20and%20Meta%2C%20the%20tips%20extend%20well%20beyond%20Silicon%20Valley%20to%20almost%20every%20white-collar%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20step%20is%20personal%3A%20figure%20out%20what%20you%20like%20to%20do.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20good%20to%20broaden%20that%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20good%20to%20be%20honest%20with%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20Bolin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBolin%20referenced%20a%20%26quot%3Bhero%20quest%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20went%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-manager-dresses-up-to-work-from-home-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20thought%20there%20would%20be%20a%20challenge%20that%20all%20the%20other%20engineers%20couldn't%20solve%20that%20he%20could%2C%20he%20said.%20Bolin%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bembarrassing%26quot%3B%20because%20there's%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20about%20ego%26quot%3B%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20this%20quest%20was%20also%20that%20he%20didn't%20love%20the%20work.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20things%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20smaller%20subset%20of%20things%20that%20I%20genuinely%20enjoy%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBolin's%20second%20step%20was%20to%20find%20out%20what's%20%26quot%3Breally%20valuable%26quot%3B%20to%20your%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20he%20uses%20the%20counterexample%20of%20his%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ads-adwords%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eat%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20yet%20again.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20stuff%20that%20I%20was%20really%20excited%20about%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20AdWords%20for%20Google%20or%20anything%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20workers%20should%20find%20the%20intersection%20between%20Bolin's%20first%20and%20second%20steps%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20lean%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20intersection%20might%20not%20be%20in%20your%20current%20workplace%2C%20something%20that%20Bolin%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bchallenge.%26quot%3B%20To%20get%20ahead%2C%20workers%20might%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Bgo%20somewhere%20else%20to%20make%20that%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20steps%20are%20consistent%2C%20no%20matter%20where%20you're%20working.%20Know%20what%20you%20want%2C%20know%20what%20your%20employer%20wants%2C%20and%20live%20in%20the%20cross-section%20of%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20that%20you%20can%20do%20that%2C%20the%20more%20successful%20you're%20going%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Bolin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20Big%20Tech%3F%20Contact%20the%20reporter%20from%20a%20non-work%20email%20and%20device%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahchandonnet%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehchandonnet%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20or%20on%20Signal%20at%20henrychand.30%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-meta-openai-employee-advice-success-big-tech-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773131521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69af351182b35e2c04dd628b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-meta-openai-employee-advice-success-big-tech-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Before%20working%20on%20OpenAI's%20Codex%2C%20Michael%20Bolin%20was%20at%20Meta%20and%20Google.%20He%20said%20he's%20learned%20a%20thing%20or%20two%20about%20making%20an%20impact%20in%20Big%20Tech.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchandonnet%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-meta-openai-employee-advice-success-big-tech-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blackpink%E2%80%99s%20Jisoo%20to%20Receive%20Madame%20Figaro%20Rising%20Star%20Award%20at%20Canneseries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773131400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236682609%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Blackpink%20member%20and%20actor%20Jisoo%20is%20set%20to%20receive%20the%20Madame%20Figaro%20Rising%20Star%20Award%20at%20Canneseries%2C%20the%20international%20series%20festival%20taking%20place%20April%2023-28%20in%20Cannes.%20The%20award%2C%20which%20honors%20a%20personality%20who%20has%20become%20a%20major%20figure%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20will%20be%20presented%20during%20the%20festival%E2%80%99s%20opening%20ceremony%20on%20April%2023.%20Past%20recipients%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A